FROM (SELECT id 
              ,trans_dt 
              ,biz_id 
              ,debit_account_no 
              ,credit_account_no 
              ,amount 
              ,status 
              ,account_date 
              ,debit_trans_id 
              ,credit_trans_id 
              ,debit_trans_type 
              ,credit_trans_type 
              ,memo 
              ,gmt_create 
              ,gmt_modified 
          FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cfc_tally_voucher 
         WHERE month >= SUBSTR('202308',1,6)
           AND status = 'S' 

       )ctv 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT account_no 
                       ,account_type 
                   FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_det_account_info_ap_pt 
                  WHERE year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4) 
                )det_deb 
    ON ctv.debit_account_no = det_deb.account_no 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT account_no 
                       ,account_type 
                   FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_det_account_info_ap_pt 
                  WHERE year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4) 
                )det_cre 
    ON ctv.credit_account_no = det_cre.account_no 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT account_no 
                       ,account_alias 
                   FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_int_account_info 
                  WHERE year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4)
                )int_deb 
    ON ctv.debit_account_no = int_deb.account_no 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT account_no 
                       ,account_alias 
                   FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_int_account_info 
                  WHERE year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4)
                )int_cre 
    ON ctv.credit_account_no = int_cre.account_no 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT id 
                       ,settle_inst_date 
                   FROM dana_cloud_dwh.ods_cfc_biz_voucher 
                  WHERE year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4) 
                )biz_vcr 
    ON ctv.biz_id = biz_vcr.id

SELECT  account_date, account_no, closing_balance
        ,CASE   WHEN account_no = '30020000000008085004' THEN today_out_amount
                ELSE today_in_amount
        END AS today_in_amount
        ,CASE   WHEN account_no = '30020000000008085004' THEN today_out_count
                ELSE today_in_count
        END AS today_in_count
        ,CASE   WHEN account_no = '30020000000008085004' THEN today_in_amount
                ELSE today_out_amount
        END AS today_out_amount
        ,CASE   WHEN account_no = '30020000000008085004' THEN today_in_count
                ELSE today_out_count
        END AS today_out_count
FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_int_account_daily
WHERE   year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4)
